snippet.textDisplay:
The difference between this version and Fareed Ayaz' version in Season 5 clearly explains the difference between Rohail Hayaty and Strings. 
Amjad Sabri did extremely well but not everything can be transformed into rock and pop music as Strings do. 
Coke Studio will never be the same without Rohail Hayatt.
